 <li>phasing out ad-hoc solutions for sourcing the model data;</li>
 <li>support model development and related projects;</li>
 <li>communication with the stakeholders in the model development and model risk management domains.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>I am looking for (expertise):</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>MSc in the field of Computer Science, Finance, Economics and/or Mathematics/Statistics;</li>
 <li>4 - 5 years of experience in a data oriented function, experience should cover both data content knowledge and technical knowledge (i.e. able to build complex sql queries to filter data);</li>
 <li>Expertise in the field of risk and/or finance is a must, expertise in statistical modelling is a pre.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong> </strong></p>
<p><strong>Personal skills</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>Strong analytical skills;</li>
 <li>Critical mind-set with respect to what is delivered;</li>
 <li>Hands on mentality with regard to data;</li>
 <li>Strong communicator;</li>
 <li>Good team player, able to contribute in a multi-cultural team;</li>
 <li>Fluency in English both written and verbal (work language).</li>
</ul>
<p>It is a full time contracting position in Amsterdam. Considering the current situation, working from home is possible for now but expect to be going to the office again when the situation allows to.</p>', 'HuxleyIT', '', NULL, 'Amsterdam', '2020-08-26 14:55:40.316745', 'competitive', 'Model Data Analyst', 'HA-33545402', 'https://www.huxley.com/nl-nl/job/kyc/HA-33545402');
