INSERT INTO public.vacancy VALUES ('07a0093a-fb32-401f-97a8-c953c2b69019', 'In fast changing markets, customers worldwide rely on Thales. Thales is a business where brilliant people from all over the world come together to share ideas and inspire each other. In aerospace, transportation, defence, security and space, our achitects design innovative solutions that make our tomorrow''s possible.
<p>Soort opdracht: Afstudeeropdracht</p>
<p>Niveau: HBO</p>
<p>Studierichting(en): Informatica, Software Engineering</p>
<p>Titel van de opdracht: Test framework for Combat Management Systems</p>
<p><b><u>About us</u></b></p>
<p>With 80.000 talents working in 68 countries, we are one of the biggest high-tech employers in the field of safety and security. In the Netherlands, where 2000 employees are based, we are located in four cities: Huizen, Delft, Eindhoven and Hengelo (HQ). Together with an extensive ecosystem of knowledge partners, customers and suppliers, we work on radars for naval vessels, cyber security solutions, transportation systems, communication equipment for land forces, cryogenic cooling solutions, research &amp; development for radar tech (in collaboration with TU Delft).<br><br>The software department of the Application Engineering cluster is responsible for the software development in Combat Management and Radar- and Optical sensors for worldwide navies- and defense systems. The work is performed in multi-disciplinary agile teams with specialists in software/system/test engineering and functional design.</p>
<p>TACTICOS is developed in a continuous integration environment. Every night all its components are automatically unit tested. Also the complete TACTICOS system is tested using the HMI with Rational Functional Tester (RFT).</p>
<p>The use of RFT and changing test strategies over time increased the complexity and maintenance effort for existing and new tests. To reduce this effort, a restructuring of the current test code is desired.</p>
<p><u>About the assignment</u></p>
<p>Develop a new test framework that provides the following improvements:</p>
<ul>
 <li>Make test scenarios independent of test application or framework (RFT, Fest-Swing…)</li>
 <li>Provide building blocks to create scenarios with limited programming knowledge/effort.</li>
 <li>Enable flexible timing control for individual test steps.</li>
 <li>Report test results in structured format that supports easy fault analysis (XML/HTML -based)</li>
</ul>
<p>Within this assignment you will develop a prototype of a test framework to demonstrate the new test features. After validation a migration path is to be provided to convert the existing test suite to the new framework and implemented for a single application.</p>
<p>You will get input from experts at Thales and use rapid prototyping (using Kanban) to create working software for us to ‘play’ with.</p>
<p><u>Affinity</u></p>
<p>Linux, Java, User Interface</p>
<p><b><u>Thales offers… </u></b></p>
<ul>
 <li>An interesting internship or graduation assignment in an international high tech environment</li>
 <li>An open and flexible working environment</li>
 <li>An excellent internship allowance</li>
 <li>Its own student association where you can participate in educational and fun activities. </li>
</ul>
<p><b><u>Interested?</u></b></p>
<p>Direct solliciteren? Gebruik dan je eigen, persoonlijke profiel om jouw interesse aan ons kenbaar te maken en kies voor ‘Apply now’.</p>
<p>Would you like to apply directly? Then click on the button ‘Apply now’ to show your interest.<br>Please keep in mind that we can only consider students who are enrolled at a school during the whole internship period for our internships and graduation assignments.</p>
<p>At Thales we provide CAREERS and not only jobs. With Thales employing 80,000 employees in 68 countries our mobility policy enables thousands of employees each year to develop their careers at home and abroad, in their existing areas of expertise or by branching out into new fields. Together we believe that embracing flexibility is a smarter way of working. Great journeys start here, apply now!</p>   <strong>Type vacature:</strong>  Intern   Vaardigheden
