<p>The assignments are performed individually or in a group. Programming those services can be done in either Java or C++. The services shall implement a REST interface and dependent on the kind of data extended with a gRPC interface for technical performance requirements.</p>
<p>Every assignment starts with the establishment of requirements, a design, an implementation and test evidence. Preferably the assignment is performed in one of our product teams using a Scrum way of working.</p>
